name: all DEG vs sham uninfected
author: Seth Barribeau
description: Differentially expressed genes under four treatments relative to sham-primed and sham-infected individuals: WNV-primed and sham-infected (Sham_C.WNVp_C), sham-primed and WNV infected (Sham_C.Sham_WNV), WNV-primed and WNV-infected (Sham_C.WNVp_WNV), sham-primed and JEV infected (Sham_C.Sham_JEV), and WNV-primed and JEV infected (Sham_C.WNVp_JEV).
source: Labs of Marcus Blagrove and Seth Barribeau (University of Liverpool)
